#X text 24 17 In this example we have eight oscillators with independent controls for frequency \, amplitude and phase. The fundamental frequency is given from random pitches and each partial's frequency is obtained from a ratio. By the dfault \, we have an inharmonic/detuned series \, which was not possible with array with the "sinesum" command and [tabread4~].;
